{"tid":985254,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"兩倍速煲劇真係爽","createTime":"2019-01-17T12:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T13:33:50.000Z","uid":115775,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fbc496b26d9d83c77485ddf5568d9087632034f3","tid":985254,"uid":115775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:24:32.000Z","msg":"以前好抗拒飛劇或者開倍速睇戲<br />\n隨住年紀愈黎愈大 時間愈黎愈少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有咁多電視劇電影動畫想睇<br />\n近排終於試左加速睇劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論日劇美劇韓劇或者係動畫 分別其實唔大 反而會因為開左加速冇咁悶 爽快好多<br />\n除左個別情況 對白太多或者經典動作場面之外 大部份情況開住兩倍速真係好多優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9fadc11dcd8f92b46a00ced6dd4762bb1bad4a","tid":985254,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:25:30.000Z","msg":"1.3至1.5 剛好"},{"pid":"d92924f047b3ea12dc626ce1c46ee645a5d36dcd","tid":985254,"uid":64296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"以前睇韓劇見又長又拖又慢所以試過倍速睇，覺得好好多"}]}